Common Troubleshooting Tools:
- ping
- traceroute
- nmap
- arp
- telnet
- openssl s_client -connect EXAMPLE.COM:443
- tcpdump/wireshark (tcpdump -v -i eth0 -w test.pcap)
- ss (Socket statistics. It allows showing information similar to netstat, ss -tuna)
      - ss -at dst :443 or dst :80
      - ss -tunap
- netstat (netstat -tulpen)
